1. Concrete Regression Flows (1/2). Local vs CI vs Farm Developer “inner loop” (fast, focused subsets). CI per-commit/per-PR runs (sanity + selected CORE tests). Nightly/weekly farm runs (CORE/STRESS/FULL tiers). Command-Line Interfaces

